{"tid":2213664,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實做人真係好攰","createTime":"2020-09-22T16:20:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T10:41:45.000Z","uid":14090,"like":22,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a1fd9d5d94c3443e0b16e80200a3fa05849fea5f","tid":2213664,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T16:20:24.000Z","msg":"自己唔開心都唔知同邊個講好 覺得自己身邊根本無一個會明白自己咁<br />\n<br />\n同女朋友講佢又好似唔多明 講多兩講又會覺得根本無乜嘢 甚至有時佢都唔知我有唔開心 佢又忙 我又忙 有時寒暄一兩句就算咁 根本就唔內心世界係點 <br />\n<br />\n有時又會覺得同佢差距好遠 自己都好努力拉近差距 但發覺大家好似唔同level咁 有時只會怪自己唔夠強壯<br />\n<br />\n做人真係好攰 好辛苦 返工已經好大壓力 放工好似仲有另一種煩惱咁 人越大就越唔開心咁"},{"pid":"460399ae446eb4d53a8f7ef86b32539587677179","tid":2213664,"uid":21355,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T16:21:45.000Z","msg":"起碼有女朋友"},{"pid":"7de4979acf32258e33bcb92431ff6ca2f7ec0d35","tid":2213664,"uid":217096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T16:22:55.000Z","msg":"上連登9up下咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f19586460e5ee84965b001a41385e8c842cf2ab","tid":2213664,"uid":247737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T16:23:09.000Z","msg":"有女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a05d955287d2b403d0382b4d8539ee89584cd30","tid":2213664,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"460399ae446eb4d53a8f7ef86b32539587677179","tid":2213664,"uid":21355,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T16:21:45.000Z","msg":"起碼有女朋友"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T16:24:19.000Z","msg":"你咁講我仲有隻貓添<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2186664e507e1f853c03b3b83d70b96c4c03e02a","tid":2213664,"uid":244358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T16:25:05.000Z","msg":"咁你有咩唔開心呀？"},{"pid":"5d34de60c3310599ff